Golfers on Golf Radio Chicago
 
 
 
                The Golfers on Golf Radio Show is talk radio for golfers.  We cover the "world of golf" with a local focus.  LIVE Radio Broadcasts in Chicago                   Golfers on Golf Radio is "on break" for the winter.  We return to the air with LIVE broadcasts in the summer golf season.   Follow our News Blog all year long!   Perfect your drive home! During the golf season, "Golfers on Golf" airs LIVE on Mondays from 6PM to 7PM on 1530AM. Or, you can catch the "podcast" on your computer anytime!  If you missed any of our live broadcasts,  click here  to replay the show on your computer!               Broadcasts and News                       Your hosts are Ed Stevenson, Bill Berger, Mike Munro, and Rory Spears.  Join the guys weekly for:   Talk from the tours (PGA, LPGA, Champions Tour, etc)  News from the Chicagoland golf community  Features including the Illinois Junior Golf Association (IJGA) "Spotlight"  Interviews with personalities and news makers from throughout the world of golf  Listener calls, FUN, and much more!   Questions? Comments? Want to talk with Bill, Mike, Rory and Ed? Call us LIVE during the show on the WJJG studio line at (708) 493-1530.    
  
  
 
 
 
