 About Golfers on Golf Radio 
 
 Golfers on Golf is a talk radio show created by golfers for golfers, broadcast live in Chicago. We cover the major tours, including the PGA Tour, but Golfers on Golf's true focus is local golf news in the Chicago area, Illinois, and greater Midwest. Features include live interviews with individuals and personalities from throughout the world of golf. 
 
 
 
 Gog Blog 
 
      Get golf news between the broadcasts with the Golfers on Golf Blog.  
 
 
 
 
 

 
  
  
 

 
 
 
 
 
  
  
  
 
 
 
